<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Section Number="0406.03" xmlns="http://StatRev.xsd"><Catchline xml:space="preserve">Organization and meetings of commission.</Catchline><SectionBody><Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">The commission shall annually select a chair from among its own membership and shall meet at least four times each year and on the call of the chair.</Text></SectionBody><History xml:space="preserve">s. 3, ch. 70-232; s. 4, ch. 78-323; ss. 6, 7, ch. 81-89; ss. 1, 4, ch. 82-46; s. 2, ch. 83-265; ss. 7, 8, ch. 87-359; s. 5, ch. 91-429; s. 26, ch. 97-103.</History></Section>